General.Name: Manet Coin
General.Description: Manet Coin is a Proof of Work/Proof of Stake cryptocurrency based on the scrypt algorithm.

ICO.Description:
MiniApps is a new AI and blockchain powered chatbot platform. MiniApps clients can easily construct chatbots/miniApps from the building blocks which are called templates. This allows users with little or no knowledge in programming to create chatbots/miniApps.

Team:

  • Vitaly Gumirov: Co-Founder. 
  • Yuri Peshkichev: Co-Founder. 
  • Peter Matyukov: Co-Founder. 

MiniApps will be holding its ICO on October 18, 2017. The ICO token supply represents 50% of the total token supply. Tokens will be available, for 0.01 ETH each at the offering. The ICO funding cap is 8,000,000 USD and is expected to end on December 19, 2017 or when the funding cap is reached.

Token Reserve Split (50%):

  • 35% Reserved for partners, community grants, and the bounty campaign;
  • 15% Reserved for the MiniApps team;
